name: Spider-Man tights
description:
The upper body performs well, while the lower body performs poorly due to material reasons。

图集基本是上半身，所以下半身裤子学习的不是很好。希望各位多发些自己跑的图让我看看效果。（电脑配置不太行，跑不了特别多的高清）。lora推荐0.8—0.9

v1.5,效果应该会比第一版本更偏向于写实，推荐用高清跑图，脚的部分有些时候会出现高跟鞋的跟，手指的部分尽量就别漏，跑的图都有点崩坏。

V1.5. The effect should be more realistic than the first version. It is recommended to use high-definition running charts. Sometimes the heels of high heels appear on the feet, and the performance of the fingers is not very good。
